OL,3,CPatients warned about filming NHS
OL,4,Cmedical care for TikTok and Instagram
OL,6,FPatients who record their NHS medical
OL,7,Ftreatment for TikTok or Instagram are
OL,8,Fputting themselves and others at risk,
OL,9,Faccording to the Society of
OL,10,FRadiographers (SoR).
OL,12,FThe trade union said filming NHS staff
OL,13,Fand treatments risked publishing other
OL,14,Fpatients' medical information and is
OL,15,Fcausing NHS staff unecessary anxiety,
OL,16,Fwhich could compromise the delivery of
OL,17,Ftreatment.
