OL,4,Cmedical care for TikTok and Instagram
OL,6,FThe SoR are calling for clear and
OL,7,Fwidespread NHS policies that prevent
OL,8,Fpatients from photographing or filming
OL,9,Fclinical procedures without permission.
OL,11,FAshley d'Aquino, a therapeutic
OL,12,Fradiographer working in London, said a
OL,13,Frising number of patients are choosing
OL,14,Fto film their own medical treatment
OL,15,Ffor social media.
