OL,6,FShe told the SoR's Annual Delegates'
OL,7,FConference that she had been
OL,8,Fapproached by other members of staff,
OL,9,Fin her capacity as union
OL,10,Frepresentative, over patients
OL,11,Frecording some of their cancer
OL,12,Ftreatment.
OL,14,FShe added: "I had one patient whose
OL,15,Frelative started filming while I was
OL,16,Ftrying to set up the treatment.
OL,18,F"It wasn't the right time ` I was
OL,19,Ftrying to focus on delivering the
OL,20,Ftreatment.
