OL,3,CPatients warned about filming NHS
OL,4,Cmedical care for TikTok and Instagram
OL,6,F"We had another member of staff who
OL,7,Fagreed to take photos for a patient.
OL,9,F"But when the patient handed over her
OL,10,Fphone, the member of staff saw that
OL,11,Fthe patient had also been covertly
OL,12,Frecording her to publish on her cancer
OL,13,Fblog.
OL,15,F"As NHS staff, we wear name badges, so
OL,16,Four names will be visible in any video.
OL,18,F"It makes people feel very
OL,19,Funcomfortable and anxious."
