OL,3,CPatients warned about filming NHS
OL,4,Cmedical care for TikTok and Instagram
OL,6,FThere is also a risk that patient's
OL,7,Ffilming their own care could
OL,8,Finadvertently film other patients in
OL,9,Fthe background.
OL,11,FThis could have wide-ranging
OL,12,Fconsequences, from breaking that
OL,13,Fpatient's confidentiality, to
OL,14,Fembarrassing the patient, or putting
OL,15,Fpatients who don't want others to know
OL,16,Ftheir location at risk.
OL,18,FAnother union member, a radiology
OL,19,Fdepartment assistant, said one
OL,20,Finstance of filming left her so
OL,21,Fstressed she couldn't sleep.
