OL,3,CPatients warned about filming NHS
OL,4,Cmedical care for TikTok and Instagram
OL,6,FWhile inserting a cannula into a
OL,7,Fcancer patient, the patient's 19-year-
OL,8,Fold daughter started filming her for
OL,9,Fsocial media without asking permission.
OL,11,F"In the next bay, a patient was having
OL,12,Fconsent taken for a virtual
OL,13,Fcolonoscopy, which is an invasive and
OL,14,Fpotentially embarrassing procedure.
OL,16,F"That could have all been recorded on
OL,17,Fthe film ` including names and dates
OL,18,Fof birth.
OL,20,F"I spent the weekend afterwards
OL,21,Fworrying: did I do my job properly?
