OL,6,FProfessor Meghana Pandit, NHS
OL,7,FEngland's co-national medical director
OL,8,Ffor secondary care, said: "We want to
OL,9,Fdo everything possible to support
OL,10,Fpatients' understanding of their
OL,11,Fdiagnosis and treatment, but it's
OL,12,Fvital that, if patients wish to record
OL,13,Fany part of their NHS care, they
OL,14,Fdiscuss this with their healthcare
OL,15,Fprofessional first and it remains for
OL,16,Fpersonal use only.
